## The Infrastructure Gap

Enterprise AI in 2026 generates output.

It does not govern decisions.

There is no structured layer between the reasoning a system produces
and the decision an executive must validate, sign, and act upon
under regulatory, financial, and operational constraints.

That gap — between AI output and governed executive decision —
is the infrastructure gap QORWAY closes.

