## What QORWAY Is

QORWAY is decision governance infrastructure.

It is the layer that sits between enterprise data and executive action.

It connects:
- structured domain knowledge
- causal reasoning
- constraint validation
- event orchestration
- sovereign execution
- feedback learning

into one governed, traceable, auditable runtime.

